ia}} [[Indira Gandhi]]\nFile:King Faisal of Saudi Arabia on on arrival ceremony welcoming 05-27-1971 (cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[Faisal of Saudi Arabia|Faisal bin Abdulaziz Al Saud]]\nFile:King Khalid 1978-2.jpg|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[Khalid of Saudi Arabia|Khalid bin Abdulaziz Al Saud]]\nFile:Pierre Trudeau (1975).jpg|{{flagicon|Canada}} [[Pierre Trudeau]]\nFile:JoeClark.jpg|{{flagicon|Canada}} [[Joe Clark]]\nFile:Juan Domingo Per\u00f3n 1973.jpg|{{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Juan Per\u00f3n]]\nFile:Isabel Martinez de Peron.jpg|{{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Isabel Mart\u00ednez de Per\u00f3n]]\nFile:Jorge Rafael Videla 1976.PNG|{{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Jorge Rafael Videla]]\nFile:President Suharto, 1993.jpg|{{flagicon|Indonesia}} '''[[Suharto]]'''\nFile:Lee Kuan Yew.jpg|{{flagicon|Singapore}} '''[[Lee Kuan Yew]]'''\nFile:PolPot.jpg|{{flagicon|Cambodia|1975}} [[Pol Pot]]\nFile:LonNol.jpg|{{flagicon|Cambodia|1970}} [[Lon Nol]]\nFile:Norodom_Sihanouk_(1983).jpg|{{flagicon|Cambodia|1954}} [[Norodom Sihanouk]]\nFile:Mohammad Reza Pahlavi (cropped).png|{{flagicon|Iran|1964}} Shah [[Mohammad Reza Pahlavi]]\nFile:Portrait of Ruhollah Khomeini By Mohammad Sayyad.jpg|{{flagicon|Iran|1964}} Ayatollah [[Ruhollah Khomeini]]\nFile:Hussein of Jordan 1997 (cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Jordan}} '''[[Hussein of Jordan]]'''\nFile:Flickr_-_Government_Press_Office_(GPO)_-_THE_NOBEL_PEACE_PRIZE_LAUREATES_FOR_1994_IN_OSLO._(cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Palestinian National Authority}} '''[[Yasser Arafat]]'''\nFile:Jomo_Kenyatta_1966-06-15.jpg|{{flagicon|Kenya}} [[Jomo Kenyatta]]\nFile:Sheikh Mujibur Rahman in 1950.jpg|{{flagicon|Bangladesh}} [[Sheikh Mujibur Rahman]]\nFile:Ziaur_Rahman_1979.jpg|{{flagicon|Bangladesh}} [[Ziaur Rahman]]\nFile:Ahmad_Hassan_el_Bakr.jpg|{{flagicon|Iraq}} [[Ahmed Hassan al-Bakr]]\nFile:Saddam_Hussain_1980_(cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Iraq}} [[Saddam Hussein]]\nFile:Omar_Torrijos_1977.jpg|{{flagicon|Panama}} '''[[Omar Torrijos]]'''\nFile:Mobutu.jpg|{{flagicon|Zaire}