am Tolbert]]\nFile:Masayoshi Ohira at Andrews AFB 1 Jan 1980 cropped 1.jpg|{{flagicon|Japan|1870}} [[Masayoshi \u014chira]]\nFile:Senipramoj Cropped.jpg|{{flagicon|Thailand}} [[Seni Pramoj]]\nFile:Bill Rowling, 1962.jpg|{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Bill Rowling]]\nFile:Eisaku Sato 1960.jpg|{{flagicon|Japan|1870}} [[Eisaku Sat\u014d]]\nFile:Adolfo Su\u00e1rez 1977 (cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Spain|1977}} [[Adolfo Su\u00e1rez]]\nFile:Tanaka Cropped.jpg|{{flagicon|Japan|1870}} [[Kakuei Tanaka]]\nFile:Bokassa portrait.jpg|{{flagicon|CAF}} [[Jean-B\u00e9del Bokassa|Jean-Bedel Bokassa]]\nFile:IbrahimAl_Hamdi.jpg|{{flagicon|North Yemen}} [[Ibrahim al-Hamdi]]\nFile:Ahmad_al-Ghashmi.jpg|{{flagicon|North Yemen}} [[Ahmad al-Ghashmi]]\nFile:Young_Saleh_of_Yemen.jpg|{{flagicon|North Yemen}} [[Ali Abdullah Saleh]]\nFile:Salim_Rubayya_Ali_(cropped).JPG|{{flagicon|South Yemen}} [[Salim Rubai Ali]]\n</gallery>\n\n===Actors / Entertainers===\n{{Div col|colwidth=18em}}\n* [[Alan Alda]]\n* [[Nancy Allen (actress)|Nancy Allen]]\n* [[Woody Allen]]\n* [[John Amos]]\n* [[Julie Andrews]]\n* [[Bea Arthur]]\n* [[Alan Arkin]]\n* [[Ed Asner]]\n* [[Barbara Bain]]\n* [[Nathalie Baye]]\n* [[Ned Beatty]]\n* [[Warren Beatty]]\n* [[Ed Begley Jr.]]\n* [[Jean-Paul Belmondo]]\n* [[John Belushi]]\n* [[Ingrid Bergman]]\n* [[Karen Black]]\n* [[Linda Blair]]\n* [[Ernest Borgnine]]\n* [[Tom Bosley]]\n* [[Peter Boyle]]\n* [[Marlon Brando]]\n* [[Beau Bridges]]\n* [[Jeff Bridges]]\n* [[Eric Braeden]]\n* [[Mel Brooks]]\n* [[Charles Bronson]]\n* [[Jim Brown]]\n* [[Yul Brynner]]\n* [[Carol Burnett]]\n* [[Ellen Burstyn]]\n* [[Richard Burton]]\n* [[Raymond Burr]]\n* [[James Caan]]\n* [[Sid Caesar]]\n* [[Michael Caine]]\n* [[Colleen Camp]]\n* [[David Carradine]]\n* [[Diahann Carroll]]\n* [[Johnny Carson]]\n* [[Lynda Carter]]\n* [[David Cassidy]]\n* [[John Cassavetes]]\n* [[Richard Chamberlain]]\n* [[Jackie Chan]]\n* [[Chevy Chase]]\n* [[Julie Christie]]\n* [[Jill Clayburgh]]\n* [[John Cleese]]\n* [[James Coburn]]\n* [[Joa